	   <tr><td colspan=2>Actually, if you want to have a Necro that start at a good location, go with dark elves, the city is almost at the heart of the entire world.<br><br>As for you having trouble with the NPC's KOS to you, what I would do is, I wouldnt leave Nektulos until about level 6-8. Once you are level 8, simply purchase the spell gather shadows. once you have that, you can travel invisible. When you travel invisible, these NPC's will have a little trouble spoting you.<br><br>Good Luck<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
