	   <tr><td colspan=2>I would like to put my 2 cents worth in on the INT need for Necro's.<br><br>INT give you additional mana, which is always a good thing.&nbsp;&nbsp;The worry about having to spend alot of time medding can be countered with the use of Dark Pact, which is a self only breeze/clarity spell.<br><br>By using DP you can cut the amount of downtime in half or more.<br><br>INT is important to intelligence based casters.<br><br>Meditate will quickly max itself out when you med, so you really don't have much control over that.<br><br>Travel safe.<br><br>Sythlor 15 years of Norrath Life.<br>&nbsp;<br>Meallen<br>Dwarven Cleric</td></tr>
